reviewText: My daughter liked the songs and the story!

Once Again this here is another Great and Amazing Dvd with Amazing Stoires about Friendship and Inspiration and even about the Importance of Listening to your Friends. THis Dvd is highly recommended and the Stories are really amazing for Friends and family to enjoy!!

This was a great DVD with five episodes that will place a smile on your childrens' faces, or at least it did mine. My girls have loved Angelina Ballerina for years now and are always excited for the next DVD that they can watch. They particularly enjoyed the Angelina and the Bandleader episode and the I Will Be a Star Music Video, but all of the episodes were fun and shared some great messages that I know that I want my daughters to learn. If you are a fan of the Angelina Ballerina books or have watched the series in the past you will love this new DVD!

*I received this for review - all opinions are my own*

My 3 year old loves Angelina ballerina!! It's a good, sweet show. She has learned the names of several dance moves, and now tries to copy them and dance all the time! I love that there are little lessons on being a good friend/sister ect...
My daughter adores this show. I've watched it through and it has a good message and I am ok with letting her watch any of the Angelina's.
